author: skillmattic
body: The ways are endless lol. Whatever your hobby is, incorporate it with KENDU and share it to the world. The community is creative and innovative. The more unique ways of sharing KENDU the better. I remember a chad came up with beer coasters with the logo and QR code on them. Every bar he visited he left the coasters. I created and printed 500 stickers with the logo, CA's, our motto, our socials, the name "Kendu Inu", join the pack phrase and a QR code. I like to travel, so I keep a stack of stickers with me wherever I go. Just have fun with it and enjoy the comradery at KENDU! Of course buying and holding forever is the best workü´°ü™ñ
